text: Lycée Camille Pissarro is a senior high school/sixth-form college in Pontoise, Val-d'Oise, France, in the Paris metropolitan area. Planning for the school began in 1953 and it was first established in 1959."Brochure historique." Lycée Camille Pissarro.
